      copy constructor
      参数:

    • Property

      public Property​(java.lang.String propertyName, java.lang.String city, double rentAmount, java.lang.String owner)
      parameterized constructor plot is defined as default plot
      参数:
      propertyName - name of the property
      city - city where the property is located
      rentAmount - rent amount
      owner - name of the owner

    • Property

      public Property​(java.lang.String propertyName, java.lang.String city, double rentAmount, java.lang.String owner, int x, int y, int width, int depth)
      parameterized constructor
      参数:
      propertyName - name of the property
      city - city where the property is located
      rentAmount - rent amount
      owner - name of the owner
      x - x coordinate of the upper left corner of the property
      y - y coordinate of the upper left corner of the property
      width - width of the property
      depth - length(vertical) of the property
